export const getDatasourceAsSaveableDataset = source => ({
  columns: source.columns,
  name: source?.datasource_name || source?.name || 'Untitled',
  dbId: source?.database?.id || source?.dbId,
  sql: source?.sql || '',
  catalog: source?.catalog,
  schema: source?.schema,
});
